---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="404 - 找不到頁面 | 拓必工作室">
  <main class="min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center space-y-8 max-w-2xl">
    <br><br>
    <p style="font-size:15em; color:#434343; font-weight:bold">
        404
      </p>
    
      <p class="text-xl text-black/50 leading-relaxed">
        抱歉，您所尋找的頁面可能已經移動、刪除，或者網址輸入有誤。
      </p>

      <div class="pt-8">
        <a 
          href="/" 
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-black text-white px-10 py-5 text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-black/80 transition-all group"
        >
          回到首頁
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            width="18" height="18" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"
          >
            <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>
